                            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #cc0000; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">Medical Discovery</p>
                            <h1 class="headline" style="margin: 0; color: #222222; font-size: 34px; line-height: 42px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: -1px;">
                                The &quot;Diabetic Parasite&quot;: Why Millions Are Turning To This Simple Home Ritual
                            </h1>
                            <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; color: #666666; font-style: italic; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; padding-top: 15px;">
