                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0 40px 30px 40px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 26px; color: #444444;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                                A groundbreaking report recently aired on <strong>60 Minutes</strong> has sent shockwaves through the medical community, identifying what researchers call a &quot;biological loophole&quot; in Type 2 Diabetes management.
